title: Dakine Excursion Glove
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2013 Excursion Glove in our Citron print.
Excursion Features:
- Insert: Gore Tex® Waterproof / Breathable insert
- Insulation: Primaloft® [ 170g ]
- Palm/Shell: Durable water repellent leather
- Shell: Nylon / Poly with DWR treatment
- Lining: 360g wool lining / 400g Pile
- Cuff Closure: Adjustable hook and loop
